{\left[x^{\prime} x+y^{\prime} y+z^{\prime} z+2 \sqrt{\left(y^{\prime} z^{\prime}+z^{\prime} x^{\prime}+x^{\prime} y^{\prime}\right)(y z+z x+x y)}\right]^{2}}
